## Key Arch Decisions

- Clean Architecture: Domain → Application → Infrastructure → API
- CQRS via MediatR (Commands/Queries separated)
- Angular 17 frontend (human-only — UX decisions not in specs)
- Auth module always human-reviewed (Azure AD security risk)
- Deploy window: Wednesday before 10:00 only
- Staging resets Sundays 03:00

## Agentization

- Target: 60% backend, 0% Angular, 0% Auth
- Budget: $30/sprint, max 5 parallel agents
- Model: claude-opus-4-7 (agent), claude-sonnet-4-6 (mid)

